//
// test/sema/width/zero_extend_expr.test — zero-extend-expression
// width fixture (T024 rollover; specs/006-m3-sema/tasks.md Phase 4a).
// The zero-extend operator `8 ' sig` (zero-extending `sig` to width
// 8) produces an expression with explicit width 8. Asserts the
// `ZeroExtendExpr` carries a `: BitVector(N)` Type suffix per
// `emit-ast-format.contract.md` Invariant 2.

// RUN: printf 'module m {\n  wire sig;\n  reg q = 8'"'"'(sig);\n}\n' > %t.nsl
// RUN: %nslc -emit=ast %t.nsl | FileCheck %s

// CHECK: (RegDecl {{.*}}name=q
// CHECK: (ZeroExtendExpr {{.*}} : BitVector({{[0-9]+}})
